  "title": "Product Manager",
  "description": "<h3>We’re looking for an experienced <strong>Product Manager</strong> to drive growth and manage leading technology product lines across Asia. In this role, you’ll build strong vendor relationships, develop go-to-market strategies, and support sales teams in winning new business.</h3>\n<p><strong>What you’ll do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage vendor/product relationships and ensure profitable growth</li>\n  <li>Develop and execute product launch and marketing strategies</li>\n  <li>Train and support sales teams and channel partners</li>\n  <li>Monitor product performance, pricing, and market trends</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What we’re looking for:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>2-3 years in product management, vendor or channel management (IT/Tech sector preferred)</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong commercial acumen and proven track record in revenue growth</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and negotiation skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We value every application, but only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thank you for considering this opportunity!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WeCruit Pte Ltd</strong> | EA License No. <strong>20C0270</strong><br>\nEA Personnel: <strong>Tan Soon Hock (Steven)</strong> | Registration No. <strong>R1109889</strong></p>",
